 payment each month that is higher than your required minimum payment.\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"}],\"nodeType\":\"paragraph\"}],\"nodeType\":\"document\"}","standardTila":"{\"nodeType\":\"document\",\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"nodeType\":\"paragraph\",\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"nodeType\":\"text\",\"value\":\"**With credit approval for qualifying purchases made on The Home Depot Consumer Credit Card. APR: 17.99% - 29.99%. Minimum interest charge: $2. See card agreement for details including APR applicable to you. Offer is valid for consumer accounts in good standing; 6 months everyday credit offer is subject to change without notice; see store for details.\",\"marks\":[],\"data\":{}}]}]}","everydayPromotion":{"__ref":"PlccPromotion:370hPRFf3LyWSNTFnRvT9T"},"appliancePromotion":{"__ref":"PlccPromotion:gl0CU8sqZZRRFrNf8m9sP"},"tieredPromotion":{"__ref":"PlccPromotion:1AGiyS1y8LyYbMz5EyEEcH"},"twelveMonthPromotion":{"__ref":"PlccPromotion:mfDpeEsY1a7UW7uvrxE3U"},"tieredAppliancePromotion":{"__ref":"PlccPromotion:Oe6YX6kMoC1CIoERUtJZv"}},"DateRange:3oLRii5eQOv2wkfrMWTjzz":{"__typename":"DateRange","id":"3oLRii5eQOv2wkfrMWTjzz","startDate":"2026-02-05T00:00","endDate":"2026-02-18T00:00"},"DateRange:6bcYQvw74x0aiHmAi5uNBy":{"__typename":"DateRange","id":"6bcYQvw74x0aiHmAi5uNBy","startDate":"2026-05-14T00:00","endDate":"2026-05-20T00:00"},"DateRange:1DLJEHfHFBTKQ9avJzgLdm":{"__typename":"DateRange","id":"1DLJEHfHFBTKQ9avJzgLdm","startDate":"2026-05-28T00:00","endDate":"2026-06-03T00:00"},"DateRange:cCZO7h0VnyoiDFD0Ni8WP":{"__typename":"DateRange","id":"cCZO7h0VnyoiDFD0Ni8WP","startDate":"2026-06-17T00:00","endDate":"2026-07-01T00:00"},"DateRange:1OrSNq7lJJOwMOofwkb8Ko":{"__typename":"DateRange","id":"1OrSNq7lJJOwMOofwkb8Ko","startDate":"2026-07-10T00:00","endDate":"2026-07-16T00:00"},"DateRange:4JGH2fAiQ7vHbv7mggcwNY":{"__typename":"DateRange","id":"4JGH2fAiQ7vHbv7mggcwNY","startDate":"2026-10-08T00:00","endDate":"2026-10-14T00:00"},"DateRange:6F9gYWhhhxha706fjQNkBt":{"__ty